'''那查格·乌德巴勒'''（{{lang-mn|Нацагийн Удвал}}，{{bd|1954年|3月5日||}}）女，[[蒙古国|蒙古国]][[后杭爱省|后杭爱省]]{{link-en|额尔德尼曼达勒|Erdenemandal, Arkhangai|额尔德尼曼达勒}}人，[[蒙古国|蒙古国]]政治人物。

==生平==
2011年起，她担任[[蒙古人民革命党_(2011年)|蒙古人民革命党]]（2011年成立）的总书记。她是2012年组建的[[阿勒坦呼亚格内阁|阿勒坦呼亚格内阁]]中的健康部部长。在[[2013年蒙古总统选举|2013年蒙古总统选举]]中，她被[[蒙古人民革命党_(2011年)|蒙古人民革命党]]提名为总统候选人，成为蒙古历史上参选的第一位女性总统候选人。<ref>{{cite web | url=http://www.wpro.who.int/mongolia/mediacentre/moh_senior_management/en/index.html | title=New Senior Officials appointed at Ministry of Health | publisher=www.wpro.who.int | accessdate=2013-06-18 | archive-date=2013-10-27 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131027152145/http://www.wpro.who.int/mongolia/mediacentre/moh_senior_management/en/index.html | dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web | url=http://online.wsj.com/article/BT-CO-20130518-700124.html | title=Three Candidates to Run for Mongolia Presidency | publisher=wsj.com | accessdate=2013-06-18 | archive-date=2014-05-17 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140517122910/http://online.wsj.com/article/BT-CO-20130518-700124.html | dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web | url=http://news.xinhuanet.com/english/world/2013-05/12/c_132376675.htm | title=First female candidate to run for Mongolian presidency | publisher=xinhuanet.com | accessdate=2013-06-18 | deadurl=yes | archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304022749/http://news.xinhuanet.com/english/world/2013-05/12/c_132376675.htm | archivedate=2016-03-04 }}</ref>乌德巴勒支持前总统[[那木巴尔·恩赫巴亚尔|那木巴尔·恩赫巴亚尔]]，后者因被控贪腐而在坐牢。<ref name=globe>{{cite news|last=Namjilsangarav|first=Ganbat|title=Mongolian President wins re-election|url=http://www.theglobeandmail.com/news/world/incumbent-mongolian-president-wins-2nd-term-on-pro-western-anti-graft-platform/article12850801/|accessdate=27 June 2013|newspaper=The Globe and Mail (AP)|date=26 June 2013|archive-date=2013-06-28|archive-url=https://archive.is/20130628040140/www.theglobeandmail.com/news/world/incumbent-mongolian-president-wins-2nd-term-on-pro-western-anti-graft-platform/article12850801/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

在2013年6月26日举行的[[2013年蒙古总统选举|2013年蒙古总统选举]]中，[[民主党_(蒙古国)|民主党]]的现任总统[[查希亚·额勒贝格道尔吉|查希亚·额勒贝格道尔吉]]最终成功连任，获得50.23％的选票。而[[蒙古人民党|蒙古人民党]]的总统候选人[[巴达玛宁布·巴特额尔登|巴达玛宁布·巴特额尔登]]获得41.97%的选票，乌德巴勒获得6.5%的选票。<ref>{{cite news|last=D.|first=Tsetseg|title=It is announced that Ts.Elbegdorj won by preliminary result|publisher=shuud.mn (in Mongolian)|url=https://www.shuud.mn/?p=250019|accessdate=June 27, 2013|date=June 27, 2013|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130629004542/http://www.shuud.mn/?p=250019|archivedate=2013-06-29}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|title=Incumbent Mongolian president wins 2nd term on pro-Western, anti-graft platform|url=http://www.washingtonpost.com/world/asia_pacific/incumbent-mongolian-president-wins-2nd-term-on-pro-western-anti-graft-platform/2013/06/26/2bbce73e-deca-11e2-ad2e-fcd1bf42174d_story.html|newspaper=Washington Post|place=Washington|accessdate=June 29, 2013|date=June 27, 2013|archive-date=2013-06-29|archive-url=https://archive.today/20130629095510/http://www.washingtonpost.com/world/asia_pacific/incumbent-mongolian-president-wins-2nd-term-on-pro-western-anti-graft-platform/2013/06/26/2bbce73e-deca-11e2-ad2e-fcd1bf42174d_story.html|dead-url=yes}}</ref>

作为健康部部长，乌德巴勒唯一引人注目的工作便是改善了监狱囚犯的医疗待遇，从而允许前总统[[那木巴尔·恩赫巴亚尔|那木巴尔·恩赫巴亚尔]]可以仅在监狱服刑少于一个月，而作为病人在第二总医院（ Second General Hospital）度过其余两年半的刑期。第二总医院是蒙古国高官们治病之所。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://mobile.time.mn/mcontent/20631.shtml?s=society&type=content|publisher=time.mn (in Mongolian)|accessdate=30 June 2013|last=D.|first=Chinguun|title=N.Enkhbayar, a prisoner or an "honorable" patient of health sector?|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131203005636/http://mobile.time.mn/mcontent/20631.shtml?s=society&type=content|archivedate=2013年12月3日}}</ref>

